Same here, setting the following environment variables in the aspire AppHost's launchSettings.json, as instructed by the OP, solves the problem for us:
```json
{
  "profiles": {
    "AppHost": {
      "environmentVariables": {
        "HTTP_PROXY": "",
        "HTTP_PROXYS": ""
      }
    }
  }
}

```
